      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/72720616-4934-11e4-956a-5254006e85c2).  Ran 18 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity-hsm.",
